node.text: This is an amazing experience - you take a boat to Cabbage Island, Maine, where you're greeted with a giant New England Clam Bake - lobsters, clams, potatoes, corn on the cob, and blueberry cake for dessert. Carnitas are normally boiled in melted fat - lard, but these special carnitas are boiled in avocado oil 🥑 making them less greasy and loaded with flavor! With @mexi_papa_adventures and @jeffrey_merrihue 

📍 When you’re in #Phoenix, don’t miss @mexicancorral #MexicanFood #Arizona #carnitas

#Tucson #Arizona #MexicanFood

node.text: The best way to get your morning started in Mae Hong Son (แม่ฮ่องสอน) is with a bowl of noodles and yellow split pea porrdige with fried tofu. Add a little chili oil, and it's warming and tasty! You'll find this at the morning market. #ShanFood #MaeHongSon #Thailand #streetfood
